While this isn't an actual review, this game has a couple of bugs I wish to bring to the developer's attention;

A) Music overlap - After quitting story mode, entering endless and then quitting to return to story again two seperate tracks continued to play over each other until the game was closed.
B) The control issue still exists, while my Xbox One controller was plugged in (On W10 64bit) I had no ability to attack to the left. Once the controller was unplugged the keyboard controls worked fine however
